headline.main: At Jaeger, There's a Return to Spirit of '84

docs.lead_paragraph: JAEGER, a company that started as a health faddist's dream and grew into a pillar of British propriety, hopes to conquer America. Its weapons are maxiskirts, capes and long culottes as well as tweed suits, skirts and coats that last forever.
